{
  "texts": [
    "The FLAME leaderboard is intended as a collaborative community effort, which we plan to update continuously as we gather more data on these foundation models.",
    "Aspects of artificial intelligence systems beyond the foundational language model are not within the scope of our study.",
    "For instance, systems such as knowledge graphs, retrieval-augmented generation (RAG), and various hybrid approaches have been shown to be beneficial in finance.",
    "However, datasets or benchmarks that focus on RAG are excluded because they assess factors beyond the language model itself (e.g., embedding quality, vector selection, and specialized metrics).",
    "Similar considerations apply to knowledge graphs."
  ]
}